                </li>
                <li class="bg-gray-800/50 p-4 rounded-lg ring-1 ring-white/10">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-white">Python (Basic to Advanced)</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">Udemy</p>
                </li>
